    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/fb56b1233fc1288fc63e5ff8dbe6c42c.poster.avif?t=1743609624\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/fb56b1233fc1288fc63e5ff8dbe6c42c.webm?t=1743609624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/fb56b1233fc1288fc63e5ff8dbe6c42c.mp4?t=1743609624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aggrolotls is an arena roguelite from top-down perspective where you are playing as tiny axolotls and have to evolve into a swarm that can take on powerful creatures from the see. Level up and pick from Upgrades that make each round feel unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/78101f0e5944ae869e83bd3632e8479e.poster.avif?t=1743609624\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/78101f0e5944ae869e83bd3632e8479e.webm?t=1743609624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/78101f0e5944ae869e83bd3632e8479e.mp4?t=1743609624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killing enemies gives you experience, which you need to level up your swarm. As you defeat bosses, you will gain access to special upgrades that change the gameplay even more drastically. This allows you to discover different builds to overcome the challenges the sea has to offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/72f1717bb70158273888e685e204c93d.poster.avif?t=1743609624\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/72f1717bb70158273888e685e204c93d.webm?t=1743609624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319000/extras/72f1717bb70158273888e685e204c93d.mp4?t=1743609624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
